'''包厘街'''（{{lang-en|Bowery}}，{{IPAc-en|icon|ˈ|b|aʊ|.|ər|i|}}，{{IPAc-en|local|ˈ|b|aʊ|.|r|i}}）是[[美國|美國]][[紐約州|紐約州]][[紐約市|紐約市]][[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]南部的一條南北向街道和小型街區。街區東至[[艾倫街_(曼哈頓)|艾倫街]]與[[下東區|下東區]]，西至包厘街與[[小意大利_(曼哈頓)|小意大利]]，南至[[運河街_(曼哈頓)|運河街]]與[[華埠_(曼哈頓)|華埠]]，北至東[[四街|四街]]與[[東村_(紐約市)|東村]]。<ref>{{cite book|author=福多爾公司 |author-link=福多爾公司 |title=Fodor's Flashmaps: New York |url= |page= |publisher=福多爾公司 |location= |date={{dts|1991||}} |ISBN= |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |author=福多爾公司 <!--|author-link=福多爾公司--> |editor-last=Dailey |editor-first=Donna |title=Fodor's See It New York City |edition=第五版 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=y5qUDg2ck7AC&pg=PA299 |page=299 |publisher=福多爾公司 |location=[[紐約|紐約]] |date={{dts|2012||}} |ISBN=978-0-8763-7136-7 |access-date={{dts|2019|9|4}} |language=en |archive-date=2016-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527152411/https://books.google.com/books?id=y5qUDg2ck7AC&pg=PA299 |dead-url=no }}</ref>從南到北，與包厘街交匯的主要或知名街道還有[[德蘭西街_(曼哈頓)|德蘭西街]]、東[[豪斯頓街|豪斯頓街]]以及{{link-en|布利克街 (曼哈頓)|Bleecker Street|布利克街}}。

包厘街得名於[[新尼德蘭|新尼德蘭]]殖民地末任[[荷蘭共和國|荷蘭]]{{link-en|新尼德蘭總幹事|Director-General of New Netherland|總幹事}}{{link-en|彼得·斯泰弗斯特|Peter Stuyvesant}}的農場，即{{lang|nl|''[[wiktionary:bouwerij|bouwerij]]''}}，街道由新尼德蘭當時更爲穩定的定居區通往農場<ref>{{cite book|last=Moscow |first=Henry |title=The Street Book: An Encyclopedia of Manhattan's Street Names and Their Origins |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xOhzui9AObUC&pg=PA29 |edition=[[復刻版|複刻本]] |page=29 |publisher={{link-en|福坦莫大學出版社|Fordham University Press}} |date={{dts|1990}} |ISBN=978-0-8232-1275-0 |quote=Bowery [–] The Namesake: Peter Stuyvesant's farm or ''bouwerij,'' to which the road led from the more settled parts of New Amsterdam. The farm's main house stood between 15th and 16th streets, just east of First Avenue. |access-date={{dts|2019|9|4}} |language=en}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[wiktionary:bowery|Bowery]]}}則[[借譯|借譯]]自這個{{link-en|現代荷蘭語|Modern Dutch}}舊詞。1760年時，這條街被叫作包厘巷（{{lang|en|Bowery Lane}}），自1807年起以現名爲人所知。<ref>{{cite book|editor-last=Brown |editor-first=Henry Collins |editor-link=:en:Henry Collins Brown |title=Valentine's Manual of Old New York |volume=7 |series=新系列 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=TN43AQAAIAAJ&pg=PA70 |page=70 |publisher=Valentine's Manual Inc. |location=[[紐約|紐約]] |date={{dts|1923||}} |quote=Bowery Lane.  The Bowery was called by this name in 1760; since 1807 known as the Bowery. |access-date={{dts|2019|9|4}} |language=en}}</ref>

